caption: b'We have invested over $25 million in @CenturyHousing\xe2\x80\x99s offering \xe2\x80\x93 an organization that supports housing needs for more than 2,000 #veterans \xe2\x80\x93 providing value and creating impact for our clients and the communities we serve. #veteransday'
